<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Featured News Detail</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheet/style.css" />
  <style>
    /* News detail (featured news card) css */
    .news-detail-hero {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 350px;
      background: url('https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3ApbcV66a_SdFxtvQhEPSy3Xnrc=/0x0:5381x3588/1520x1013/filters:focal(2261x1364:3121x2224):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/74102919/2217002424.0.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .news-detail-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }

    .news-detail-title {
      position: relative;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 3;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem 1rem 1rem;
      font-family: 'Oswald', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .news-detail-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      color: #131313;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      z-index: 3;
      position: relative;
    }

    .news-detail-content {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-top: -60px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    
    .news-detail-video {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      background: #eee;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 250px;
    }

    .news-detail-recommended {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 3rem auto 0 auto;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  <div class="news-detail-hero">
    <div class="news-detail-overlay"></div>
    <div class="news-detail-title">Salah wins Golden Boot in record-setting season</div>
  </div>
  <div class="news-detail-meta">
    <img src="https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/i/columnists/full/ohanlon_ryan.png&h=80&w=80&scale=crop" style="width:32px; height:32px; border-radius:50%;">By Ryan O'Hanlon
    <span>â€¢</span>
    <span>25 May 2025 16:28</span>
  </div>

  <!-- News Detail Content -->
  <div class="news-detail-content">
    <p>Mohamed Salah finished six goals clear of second-placed Alexander Isak and registered six assists more than Isak's Newcastle United teammate Jacob Murphy.</p>
    <p>Salah capped off his incredible season by winning the Premier League Golden Boot and Playmaker of the Season awards as well as breaking the record for the most combined goals and assists in a 38-game season.</p>
    <p>He now has the joint-highest number of Golden Boot wins (4) along with former Arsenal forward Theirry Henry.</p>
    <p>His 84th-minute goal during Sunday's 1-1 draw at Anfield rounded off what has been a remarkable individual campaign.</p>
    <div class="news-detail-video">
      <!-- Video container placeholder-->
      <iframe width="100%" height="250" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uuz1wggsGCU" title="YouTube video" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    <p>"It's incredible. Last time we did not have the chance to lift the [Premier League] trophy in front of the Kop, today we have the chance," Salah told Sky Sports.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Recommended Section -->
  <div class="news-detail-recommended">
    <h4 class="mb-3">Recommended:</h4>
    <div class="row g-3">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <div style="background:#eee; height:140px; border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;">
            <img src="#" alt="image">
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h6 class="card-title">Watch United v ASEAN All-Stars Live</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <div style="background:#eee; height:140px; border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;">
            <img src="#" alt="image">
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h6 class="card-title">Premier League - Summer transfer windows</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Redirect to News Page-->
  <div class="text-center my-4">
    <a href="/news" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Back to News</a>
  </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 